@page
@model Register50MileModel


<h2><b>Wildspire 50 Mile — “Thunder Basin 50M”</b></h2>
<p>Distance: 50.5km/50 miles<br />
Elevation Gain: 2,680 m<br />
Difficulty: Very Hard
</p>
<br />
<p> Start Time: 6:30 am</p>
<br />
<h3><b>Course Description</b></h3>
<p>50 Mile Thunder Basin
Our signature ultra: 80+ kilometers of wild, remote, soul-stirring mountain terrain. Long climbs, sweeping ridges, and quiet valleys make this a rite of passage for any ultrarunner.
</p>
<p><b>Start/Finish: Wildspire Base Camp</b><br />
<b>•	Miles 0-6 (KM 0-10):</b>
Same start as 50K to Highline Traverse, Aid Station #1 at Mile 6
<br />
<b>•	Miles 6-13:</b>
Descent into Deepwater Gorge, Rope-assisted section at Mile 11.5, Aid Station #2 at Mile 13
<br />
<b>•	Miles 13-20:</b>
Long grind up Thunder Summit, Highest point of all races (2,330 m elevation), Exposure + windy ridge crossings
<br />
<b>•	Miles 20-27:</b>
Fast descent along Wyrmback Ridge, Aid Station #3 at Mile 26.7
<br />
<b>•	Miles 27-34:</b>
Enter Thunder Basin Grasslands, Gentle rollers but fully exposed heat
<br />
<b>•	Miles 34-40:</b>
Climb South Spire Pass (+500 m), Aid Station #4 at Mile 39
<br />
<b>•	Miles 40-50:</b>
Rejoin 50K loop for final 10 miles, Long descent, then last climb over Pinecap Hill, Final 2 miles on smooth singletrack to finish


</p>
<br />
<h3>Price: $200</h3>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
    <form method="post">
    <div asp-validation-summary="ModelOnly" class="text-danger"></div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label asp-for="FirstName" class="control-label"></label>
                <input asp-for="FirstName" class="form-control" />
                <span asp-validation-for="FirstName" class="text-danger"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label asp-for="LastName" class="control-label"></label>
                <input asp-for="LastName" class="form-control" />
                <span asp-validation-for="LastName" class="text-danger"></span>
            </div>
            <br />
            <p>Shirt Size</p>
            <div class="form-check">
                <input asp-for="ShirtSize" class="form-check-input" type="radio" value="1" checked>
                <label class="form-check-label">S</label>
                <span asp-validation-for="ShirtSize" class="text-danger"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check">
                <input asp-for="ShirtSize" class="form-check-input" type="radio" value="2">
                <label class="form-check-label">M</label>
                <span asp-validation-for="ShirtSize" class="text-danger"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check">
                <input asp-for="ShirtSize" class="form-check-input" type="radio" value="3">
                <label class="form-check-label">L</label>
                <span asp-validation-for="ShirtSize" class="text-danger"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check">
                <input asp-for="ShirtSize" class="form-check-input" type="radio" value="4">
                <label class="form-check-label">XL</label>
                <span asp-validation-for="ShirtSize" class="text-danger"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check">
                <input asp-for="ShirtSize" class="form-check-input" type="radio" value="5">
                <label class="form-check-label">XXL</label>
                <span asp-validation-for="ShirtSize" class="text-danger"></span>
            </div>
            <br />
            <div class="form-group">
                <label asp-for="Gender" class="control-label"></label>
                <input asp-for="Gender" class="form-control" />
                <span asp-validation-for="Gender" class="text-danger"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label asp-for="Email" class="control-label"></label>
                <input asp-for="Email" class="form-control" />
                <span asp-validation-for="Email" class="text-danger"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label asp-for="Age" class="control-label"></label>
                <input asp-for="Age" class="form-control" />
                <span asp-validation-for="Age" class="text-danger"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <input type="submit" value="Submit" class="btn btn-primary" />
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

@if(Model.FirstName !=string.Empty){
    <p>Thank you @Model.FirstName for registering for the Wildspire 50 Mile Thunder Basin.</p>
}
